#: ../../../compiler/lowering-pipeline.md:98
msgid "Type Conversion"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../compiler/lowering-pipeline.md:100
msgid ""
"Before operations can be converted, their types must be converted. LLVM's "
"type system is deliberately simpler than Rust's -- there is no signedness on "
"integers, no tuples, no enums, no fat pointers. Everything must be flattened."
msgstr ""

